SELECT (COUNT(?uri) as ?c) WHERE {
  ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 .
  ?uri wdt:P144 ?p .
  ?uri wdt:P674 ?character .
  FILTER (?p = wdt:P144 || ?p = wdt:P674)
}

BIND(Q11424 AS ?filmType)
BIND("James Bond" AS ?entity)

ORDER BY ?c DESC
